Products List (POST) and Product By ID (GET)
Product
This response body has these new properties.
additionalFields—Key-value pair of additional standard or custom fields with their values.
catalogs—List of the associated catalogs.
Bulk Products Details (POST) and Product By ID (GET)
Product Classification
This response body has these new properties.
code—Code of the product classification record.
name—Name of the product classification record.
status—Status of the product classification record.
